help:
Configuration file generation tool. To generate:
1. Configuration bitstream (default operation)
    --aes_key={AES key binary file} --signing_key={input .pem}
    <input .bitasm> <output .cfgbit>
2. Signing private PEM
    --operation=gen_private_pem --{no_passphrase}
    --passphase={passphase or text file}
    --signing_key=<prime256v1|rsa2048> <output .pem>
3. Signing public PEM
    --operation=gen_public_pem --passphase={passphase or text file}
    <input .pem> <output .pem>
